00:01:38,800 --> 00:01:39,320
I'm

3
00:01:40,360 --> 00:01:41,420
planning to leave.

4
00:01:42,280 --> 00:01:43,800
I don't know when I'll be back.

5
00:01:43,800 --> 00:01:45,360
Or if I'll ever come back.

6
00:01:45,960 --> 00:01:47,020
So it works out that

7
00:01:48,600 --> 00:01:49,860
my house will be empty.

8
00:01:50,200 --> 00:01:51,530
It might as well be used.

9
00:01:51,920 --> 00:01:53,360
You, Bao, and Xinxin

10
00:01:54,720 --> 00:01:56,320
can stay there comfortably.

11
00:01:59,640 --> 00:02:00,300
I'd like to,

12
00:02:01,440 --> 00:02:03,240
but I'm afraid Xinxin won't agree.

13
00:02:03,240 --> 00:02:04,080
Tell Xinxin

14
00:02:04,880 --> 00:02:06,800
that you bought it.

15
00:02:07,680 --> 00:02:09,840
If she thinks you bought it for them, she'll agree.

16
00:02:09,840 --> 00:02:12,170
I'm broke now. Where would I get the money?

17
00:02:13,680 --> 00:02:14,210
Qin Gang,

18
00:02:15,360 --> 00:02:17,560
we all teach our children

19
00:02:17,720 --> 00:02:18,850
that lying is wrong,

20
00:02:19,160 --> 00:02:21,280
but I'm a few years older than you.

21
00:02:22,280 --> 00:02:23,410
I've always thought

22
00:02:24,480 --> 00:02:26,920
that to make our families' lives better,

23
00:02:28,280 --> 00:02:31,360
telling a few lies sometimes is no big deal.

24
00:02:32,400 --> 00:02:33,329
Don't you agree?

25
00:02:33,640 --> 00:02:36,240
Take it. They'll be more comfortable this way.

26
00:03:05,120 --> 00:03:05,680
Sis.

27
00:03:07,920 --> 00:03:08,360
Sis.

28
00:03:10,040 --> 00:03:10,480
No, sis.

29
00:03:10,480 --> 00:03:11,600
What are you doing?

30
00:03:12,320 --> 00:03:14,000
Qin Gang, I've let you down.

31
00:03:14,360 --> 00:03:16,160
Do you still consider me your sister?

32
00:03:16,160 --> 00:03:16,760
Of course.

33
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:19,800
Kaiyang has indeed wronged you.

34
00:03:20,120 --> 00:03:22,680
Look at how much money you've lost because of him.

35
00:03:22,680 --> 00:03:24,810
He's now received his due punishment.

36
00:03:25,120 --> 00:03:26,520
I have no other requests.

37
00:03:26,600 --> 00:03:28,840
I only ask that you forgive him.

38
00:03:29,079 --> 00:03:32,340
For Xinxin's sake, please don't hold a grudge against him.

39
00:03:32,880 --> 00:03:34,880
I've got a job now.

40
00:03:35,040 --> 00:03:36,440
I can run a small business

41
00:03:36,600 --> 00:03:38,460
and make 20,000 to 30,000 a month.

42
00:03:39,280 --> 00:03:41,740
I'll bring you the money on time every month.

43
00:03:41,760 --> 00:03:43,320
As long as I'm still breathing,

44
00:03:43,320 --> 00:03:44,160
I will pay back

45
00:03:44,440 --> 00:03:45,680
all of this money.

46
00:03:46,960 --> 00:03:48,400
Sis, I can't take this money.

47
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:49,640
We're family.

48
00:03:49,640 --> 00:03:51,900
There's no such thing as debt between us.

49
00:03:51,960 --> 00:03:52,360
Well...

50
00:03:52,360 --> 00:03:52,890
Besides,

51
00:03:53,920 --> 00:03:56,320
my brother-in-law was deceived by Liu Wei.

52
00:03:57,400 --> 00:04:00,000
Once Liu Wei is caught and the money recovered,

53
00:04:00,720 --> 00:04:02,250
we can sort everything out.

54
00:04:02,680 --> 00:04:04,800
Whoever made the mistake should bear the responsibility.

55
00:04:04,800 --> 00:04:06,160
So Kaiyang was at fault?

56
00:04:06,400 --> 00:04:08,320
I should be responsible for Kaiyang's mistakes?

57
00:04:08,320 --> 00:04:09,720
You must take this money.

58
00:04:09,920 --> 00:04:12,280
Otherwise, I won't be able to live with myself.

59
00:04:12,280 --> 00:04:14,010
Sis, I can't accept this money.

60
00:04:15,840 --> 00:04:16,200
Sis.

61
00:04:16,880 --> 00:04:19,010
Don't give us money. I still have some.

62
00:04:19,600 --> 00:04:20,839
You've just started your business.

63
00:04:20,839 --> 00:04:22,370
It's not easy to make money.

64
00:04:23,200 --> 00:04:24,660
That's a separate matter.

65
00:04:24,880 --> 00:04:26,540
If he doesn't take this money,

66
00:04:26,680 --> 00:04:28,880
I'll feel guilty for the rest of my life.

67
00:04:29,200 --> 00:04:29,660
Take it.

68
00:04:32,920 --> 00:04:33,720
Alright, sis.

69
00:04:34,480 --> 00:04:35,540
I'll take the money

70
00:04:37,159 --> 00:04:38,560
and let Xinxin manage it.

71
00:04:41,520 --> 00:04:43,280
When the police catch Liu Wei

72
00:04:43,880 --> 00:04:46,740
and recover the company's money, we'll talk again.

73
00:04:46,920 --> 00:04:50,159
Money isn't important to me right now.

74
00:04:51,480 --> 00:04:54,080
What's important is Xinxin, Xiaobao,

75
00:04:55,040 --> 00:04:55,840
and all of you.

76
00:04:56,840 --> 00:04:59,400
You are what matters most to me now.

77
00:05:08,880 --> 00:05:09,880
Ultraman.

78
00:05:11,800 --> 00:05:13,240
So cool, really.

79
00:05:14,360 --> 00:05:15,760
So cool, bro.

80
00:05:16,960 --> 00:05:18,400
So cool, really.

81
00:05:19,600 --> 00:05:22,130
It doesn't matter if the car looks cool or not.

82
00:05:22,200 --> 00:05:24,240
As long as it drives well. Let me tell you.

83
00:05:24,240 --> 00:05:26,300
I bought it secondhand from someone.

84
00:05:26,400 --> 00:05:27,200
It's a used car.

85
00:05:27,200 --> 00:05:28,560
But it's never given me any trouble.

86
00:05:28,560 --> 00:05:30,820
Just take good care of it when it's yours.

87
00:05:30,840 --> 00:05:32,360
Don't worry, I'll definitely treat it

88
00:05:32,360 --> 00:05:33,820
like my first girlfriend.

89
00:05:34,680 --> 00:05:36,880
Wait, are you really giving me this car?

90
00:05:38,440 --> 00:05:39,900
I might not be coming back.

91
00:05:40,600 --> 00:05:41,520
Look, this car of mine

92
00:05:41,520 --> 00:05:43,960
is just a piece of scrap metal sitting in the garage anyway.

93
00:05:43,960 --> 00:05:45,020
Just use it for now.

94
00:05:45,080 --> 00:05:46,000
When I leave,

95
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:48,330
I'll clean it up a bit and give you the keys.

96
00:05:49,240 --> 00:05:49,570
Wait.

97
00:05:52,280 --> 00:05:53,840
No, I think...

98
00:05:54,760 --> 00:05:56,760
You're giving me such a cool car.

99
00:05:58,040 --> 00:06:00,440
I feel like you have something else going on.

100
00:06:00,440 --> 00:06:02,970
Yes, not just the car but also that apartment.

101
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:04,940
The... the apartment too?

102
00:06:05,840 --> 00:06:08,280
Oh my god, bro!

103
00:06:10,080 --> 00:06:11,940
You're giving me your apartment!

104
00:06:12,120 --> 00:06:13,920
You're like my second parents!

105
00:06:15,320 --> 00:06:15,960
I...

106
00:06:15,960 --> 00:06:17,620
Thank you so much, I really...

107
00:06:18,680 --> 00:06:19,200
Buddy.

108
00:06:19,840 --> 00:06:21,500
I'm sorry, I shouldn't laugh.

109
00:06:21,880 --> 00:06:23,940
Buddy, let me finish what I'm saying.

110
00:06:24,040 --> 00:06:26,480
I'm not giving you the car right now.

111
00:06:26,840 --> 00:06:27,880
As for the apartment, I want you to

112
00:06:27,880 --> 00:06:29,560
convince Wan Xinxin, Qin Gang, and Bao to

113
00:06:29,560 --> 00:06:31,000
move into my apartment.

114
00:06:31,400 --> 00:06:32,560
The studio is too damp now.

115
00:06:32,560 --> 00:06:34,290
It's not good for their health.

116
00:06:37,240 --> 00:06:37,970
I feel dirty.

117
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:38,880
I'm sorry.

118
00:06:43,520 --> 00:06:45,920
Wait, you're giving the apartment to them?

119
00:06:46,560 --> 00:06:49,000
What if Wan Xinxin doesn't agree?

120
00:06:50,600 --> 00:06:53,120
That's why I'm asking you, since you're Wan Xinxin's best friend,

121
00:06:53,120 --> 00:06:53,640
right?

122
00:06:53,880 --> 00:06:55,280
Please help me convince her.

123
00:06:55,280 --> 00:06:55,810
Besides,

124
00:06:56,880 --> 00:06:57,940
to be quite honest,

125
00:06:58,760 --> 00:07:00,690
whether I'm with Wan Xinxin or not,

126
00:07:01,200 --> 00:07:03,200
I really want her to have a good life.

127
00:07:04,040 --> 00:07:06,240
I'm counting on you with the apartment. Thank you so much.

128
00:07:06,240 --> 00:07:08,640
And when the time comes, I'll clean up the car

129
00:07:08,640 --> 00:07:09,920
and give you the keys before I leave.

130
00:07:09,920 --> 00:07:12,320
I have something to do. Get yourself a taxi.

131
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:13,860
Come on, give me a ride.

132
00:07:15,280 --> 00:07:15,600
Bro.

133
00:07:17,840 --> 00:07:19,040
Let me experience it.

134
00:07:22,840 --> 00:07:23,570
It's so cool.

135
00:07:26,840 --> 00:07:28,240
I didn't bring any money.

136
00:07:37,480 --> 00:07:37,940
Qin Gang

137
00:07:39,120 --> 00:07:40,450
What are you doing here?

138
00:07:41,400 --> 00:07:42,680
It's too stuffy in the gallery.

139
00:07:42,680 --> 00:07:44,480
I brought Xiaobao out for a walk.

140
00:07:44,720 --> 00:07:46,560
When I got back to the gallery and saw you weren't there,

141
00:07:46,560 --> 00:07:47,960
my heart started racing.

142
00:07:48,280 --> 00:07:49,920
Please don't scare me like that.

143
00:07:49,920 --> 00:07:50,650
Don't worry.

144
00:07:51,920 --> 00:07:53,580
I'm really enjoying life now.

145
00:07:54,159 --> 00:07:55,690
I won't do anything stupid.

146
00:07:57,159 --> 00:07:58,090
That's a relief.

147
00:07:58,880 --> 00:07:59,480
By the way,

148
00:08:00,320 --> 00:08:01,850
I was just about to tell you.

149
00:08:01,920 --> 00:08:04,240
We really can't live in this gallery anymore.

150
00:08:04,240 --> 00:08:04,800
Look,

151
00:08:05,640 --> 00:08:07,880
those are the clothes you washed a couple days ago, right?

152
00:08:07,880 --> 00:08:10,410
I checked and they're already getting moldy.

153
00:08:10,520 --> 00:08:11,320
It's too damp.

154
00:08:12,120 --> 00:08:14,120
I haven't been in the mood to paint lately,

155
00:08:14,120 --> 00:08:15,720
and I haven't made any money.

156
00:08:15,880 --> 00:08:17,640
I'll start painting right away.

157
00:08:17,640 --> 00:08:18,880
Once I earn some money,

158
00:08:18,880 --> 00:08:20,200
we'll rent an apartment.

159
00:08:20,200 --> 00:08:22,260
Then you can live there with the baby.

160
00:08:26,840 --> 00:08:28,970
Look at you, you're barely holding up.

161
00:08:29,720 --> 00:08:31,120
I just have a slight cold.

162
00:08:31,600 --> 00:08:32,400
It's nothing.

163
00:08:33,120 --> 00:08:34,580
Let me suggest something.

164
00:08:34,840 --> 00:08:35,640
How about

165
00:08:36,320 --> 00:08:38,250
we move to Huaming's place for now?

166
00:08:38,840 --> 00:08:40,240
He's gone anyway,

167
00:08:41,520 --> 00:08:43,520
and the house is just sitting empty.

168
00:08:44,800 --> 00:08:46,400
I won't go back to live there.

169
00:08:53,240 --> 00:08:54,170
You have a fever.

170
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:56,730
I might just have a slight cold.

171
00:08:56,840 --> 00:08:59,080
I'll take some medicine when I get back. It's really nothing.

172
00:08:59,080 --> 00:08:59,400
Let's go.

173
00:08:59,400 --> 00:09:00,200
No.

174
00:09:00,520 --> 00:09:01,760
Let's go to the hospital right away.

175
00:09:01,760 --> 00:09:03,620
Come on, let's go to the hospital.

176
00:09:09,760 --> 00:09:10,520
Slow down.

177
00:09:11,240 --> 00:09:13,200
Watch your hands.

178
00:09:14,160 --> 00:09:15,840
Yes, this way.

179
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:17,160
Behind the fridge.

180
00:09:17,520 --> 00:09:18,520
Get out of the way.

181
00:09:20,040 --> 00:09:21,240
Why are you so strong?

182
00:09:21,960 --> 00:09:24,960
I've been helping you all this time and I'm exhausted.

183
00:09:25,840 --> 00:09:26,960
Aren't you young?

184
00:09:27,160 --> 00:09:28,600
I can do this kind of work by myself.

185
00:09:28,600 --> 00:09:29,800
Go do something else.

186
00:09:29,920 --> 00:09:31,520
Come on, how can you say that?

187
00:09:32,040 --> 00:09:33,840
I didn't bring any money during the day.

188
00:09:33,840 --> 00:09:35,570
You made me come back by myself.

189
00:09:35,600 --> 00:09:38,130
You're killing me with exhaustion, you know?

190
00:09:38,520 --> 00:09:40,160
What are you trying to achieve here?

191
00:09:40,160 --> 00:09:41,620
Going to all this trouble.

192
00:09:41,680 --> 00:09:44,120
I've been talking to you all this time for nothing.

193
00:09:44,120 --> 00:09:45,720
Fine. You ask me, I'll ask you too.

194
00:09:45,720 --> 00:09:47,040
You're also Wan Xinxin's friend.

195
00:09:47,040 --> 00:09:49,600
So what are you after if you're not taking any money?

196
00:09:49,600 --> 00:09:50,080
I...

197
00:09:50,200 --> 00:09:52,060
Do you have to be after something?

198
00:09:52,960 --> 00:09:53,960
I understand now.

199
00:09:54,920 --> 00:09:56,640
Your highest level of love is

200
00:09:57,560 --> 00:09:58,220
letting go.

201
00:09:58,440 --> 00:10:01,300
Another highest level is defeating your opponent.

202
00:10:01,680 --> 00:10:02,160
Phone.

203
00:10:02,480 --> 00:10:02,960
Here.

204
00:10:03,200 --> 00:10:04,440
Where's the phone?

205
00:10:04,440 --> 00:10:05,160
TV.

206
00:10:06,040 --> 00:10:06,770
Television.

207
00:10:08,160 --> 00:10:08,960
It's so heavy.

208
00:10:11,360 --> 00:10:11,820
Weimin.

209
00:10:13,320 --> 00:10:16,160
Huaming, Wan Xinxin just came in for a checkup.

210
00:10:17,120 --> 00:10:19,000
Nothing serious, just a cold.

211
00:10:19,920 --> 00:10:21,980
Okay, wait for me. I'll go right away.

212
00:10:22,200 --> 00:10:23,320
Can you help me with this?

213
00:10:23,320 --> 00:10:24,480
I'll handle it.

214
00:10:25,120 --> 00:10:25,840
This...

215
00:10:26,960 --> 00:10:28,440
You're not taking care of it anymore?

216
00:10:28,440 --> 00:10:30,880
Your highest level of love is just hugging?

217
00:10:32,240 --> 00:10:33,440
No, where did I put it?

218
00:10:38,600 --> 00:10:39,130
Qin Gang.

219
00:10:42,640 --> 00:10:43,770
How is Xinxin doing?

220
00:10:44,040 --> 00:10:45,840
She's much better, but still has a slight fever.

221
00:10:45,840 --> 00:10:47,440
What about the moving plans?

222
00:10:47,520 --> 00:10:50,250
Yes, I was just about to tell you that I'm thinking

223
00:10:50,280 --> 00:10:51,540
of moving in tomorrow.

224
00:10:51,560 --> 00:10:52,920
That's fine. Do you need my help?

225
00:10:52,920 --> 00:10:54,080
No, don't show up.

226
00:10:54,280 --> 00:10:56,810
If you appear, Xinxin will be even more upset.

227
00:10:56,960 --> 00:10:59,400
Look, why do you care whether Xinxin likes it or not?

228
00:10:59,400 --> 00:10:59,930
Qin Gang,

229
00:11:00,400 --> 00:11:01,960
just pack everything up,

230
00:11:02,080 --> 00:11:02,840
move in first,

231
00:11:02,840 --> 00:11:03,720
and she'll have to accept it

232
00:11:03,720 --> 00:11:05,250
whether she likes it or not.

233
00:11:05,960 --> 00:11:06,490
Alright,

234
00:11:06,600 --> 00:11:08,600
I'll carry her over here if I have to.

235
00:11:10,000 --> 00:11:11,320
Yes, this is very important.

236
00:11:11,320 --> 00:11:12,480
When you go back, since Xinxin

237
00:11:12,480 --> 00:11:14,280
might have a viral cold,

238
00:11:14,560 --> 00:11:15,760
you need to keep her and Bao

239
00:11:15,760 --> 00:11:17,290
separated from each other.

240
00:11:17,760 --> 00:11:18,640
Yes, got it.

241
00:11:18,840 --> 00:11:20,520
My phone is on 24 hours a day.

242
00:11:20,520 --> 00:11:22,280
Call me directly if anything happens.

243
00:11:22,280 --> 00:11:22,720
Okay,

244
00:11:23,040 --> 00:11:23,600
let's head back now.

245
00:11:23,600 --> 00:11:24,260
Sure thing.

246
00:11:53,080 --> 00:11:54,120
Is there anything else?

247
00:11:54,120 --> 00:11:54,780
That's all.

248
00:11:56,840 --> 00:11:59,240
Don't just sit there. Let's clean up first.

249
00:11:59,840 --> 00:12:01,170
Let me rest for a moment.

250
00:12:01,400 --> 00:12:02,720
We need to hurry up a bit.

251
00:12:02,720 --> 00:12:05,250
I don't want Xinxin to see me when she arrives.

252
00:12:09,240 --> 00:12:10,170
What's the rush?

253
00:12:16,960 --> 00:12:20,090
It's fine. Sit down and let me explain some things to you.

254
00:12:24,840 --> 00:12:26,360
This is the utility card.

255
00:12:26,360 --> 00:12:28,080
Water, electricity, and gas are all paid with this card.

256
00:12:28,080 --> 00:12:29,920
I've already paid for this month.

257
00:12:29,920 --> 00:12:31,240
I've linked it to my bank card.

258
00:12:31,240 --> 00:12:32,280
You don't need to worry about it.

259
00:12:32,280 --> 00:12:33,340
This is a spare key.

260
00:12:35,760 --> 00:12:36,560
And also...

261
00:12:37,520 --> 00:12:38,400
There's a notebook in here.

262
00:12:38,400 --> 00:12:39,600
I've written down Xinxin's...

263
00:12:39,600 --> 00:12:41,260
All of her habits are in there.

264
00:12:43,240 --> 00:12:43,700
Also...

265
00:12:44,560 --> 00:12:46,000
Oh right, the kitchen...

266
00:12:46,240 --> 00:12:47,800
There are two cabinets in the kitchen

267
00:12:47,800 --> 00:12:50,460
with three thermal cookers on the bottom shelf.

268
00:12:50,760 --> 00:12:51,600
The first pot

269
00:12:51,600 --> 00:12:53,280
is for your regular cooking.

270
00:12:53,760 --> 00:12:55,360
And these two are for making soup.

271
00:12:55,360 --> 00:12:57,480
Actually, Xinxin isn't too picky about food.

272
00:12:57,480 --> 00:12:58,520
She likes drinking soup.

273
00:12:58,520 --> 00:13:00,720
She prefers stronger flavors, but don't listen to her.

274
00:13:00,720 --> 00:13:01,720
Don't indulge her.

275
00:13:01,720 --> 00:13:03,250
Make the soup a bit lighter.

276
00:13:03,920 --> 00:13:04,640
Also.

277
00:13:05,680 --> 00:13:07,720
Right, the baby is still very young.

278
00:13:07,840 --> 00:13:09,900
So try not to use the air conditioner.

