284
00:13:21,080 --> 00:13:21,360
Yes.

285
00:13:22,200 --> 00:13:22,730
And also.

286
00:13:31,160 --> 00:13:31,960
These are some

287
00:13:33,400 --> 00:13:35,240
basic medications I've prepared.

288
00:13:35,240 --> 00:13:38,040
I've marked all the expiration dates here for you.

289
00:13:38,200 --> 00:13:38,680
And

