295
00:13:55,160 --> 00:13:57,220
I don't really need this key anymore.

296
00:13:58,320 --> 00:13:59,320
Keep it as a spare.

297
00:14:03,000 --> 00:14:04,480
Also...

298
00:14:05,680 --> 00:14:06,280
What else?

299
00:14:08,760 --> 00:14:09,490
I'm leaving.

300
00:14:42,360 --> 00:14:42,960
Huaming.

301
00:14:45,960 --> 00:14:46,600
I miss you.

302
00:14:50,880 --> 00:14:52,840
