304
00:15:02,360 --> 00:15:04,080
Please come back quickly.

305
00:15:05,560 --> 00:15:06,840
I'm begging you.

306
00:15:30,440 --> 00:15:30,800
Come.

307
00:15:37,440 --> 00:15:38,040
Come in.

308
00:15:39,600 --> 00:15:42,260
Qin Gang, I should go back to stay at the gallery.

309
00:15:42,520 --> 00:15:43,680
No, Xinxin.

310
00:15:44,560 --> 00:15:45,760
You're still sick.

311
00:15:46,320 --> 00:15:47,920
Stay here and rest properly.

312
00:15:48,760 --> 00:15:50,280
Let me make you something to eat.

313
00:15:50,280 --> 00:15:50,610
Here.

314
00:16:01,160 --> 00:16:02,000
Don't just stand there.

315
00:16:02,000 --> 00:16:03,240
Sit down.

316
00:16:06,800 --> 00:16:07,920
Take a rest here.

317
00:16:08,760 --> 00:16:09,960
Stop fussing around.

318
00:16:10,280 --> 00:16:11,810
I'll put the child to sleep.

319
00:16:13,640 --> 00:16:15,100
You should rest well here.

320
00:16:15,360 --> 00:16:16,960
I'll go put Xiaobao to sleep.

321
00:16:17,000 --> 00:16:18,730
I'll make you something to eat.

322
00:16:38,840 --> 00:16:39,560
Stop hiding.

323
00:16:39,560 --> 00:16:40,680
I'm not hiding from you.

324
00:16:40,680 --> 00:16:41,340
You're not?

325
00:16:41,440 --> 00:16:41,880
No.

