00:17:39,720 --> 00:17:40,850
I can't cook either.

329
00:17:41,480 --> 00:17:43,610
I boiled some eggs for you to eat first.

330
00:17:47,000 --> 00:17:47,720
Let me try.

331
00:17:51,520 --> 00:17:52,480
What's going on?

332
00:17:53,120 --> 00:17:54,760
Didn't your fever break this afternoon?

333
00:17:54,760 --> 00:17:56,040
Why is it back now?

334
00:17:57,760 --> 00:17:58,890
It's okay, Qin Gang.

335
00:17:59,720 --> 00:18:02,450
